						               													<description>A complete kit to organize a puzzling escape game evening with friends, in one of the most oppressive worlds: that of psychiatric hospitals. The director of the asylum has been kidnapped by a madman: your team of psychiatrists has one hour to find him by following the rules imposed by the psychopath. But are you sure that you and your colleagues are not suffering from serious disorders?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;As a young ambitious psychiatrist, you applied for lectures from eminent Professor Wise. He invited you to meet him in his Asylum, on island Asylum (aka: Psy Island).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Prof. Wise and you were discussing in his office, when an issue with a dangerous patient occurred. Few minutes after Prof. leaving, you hear the office's door locking...&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Escape game &amp;ndash; Psy Island, the game master (the dangerous patient, aka: Psy Island's angel) choose and hide every clues and enigmas, before the play. All along the play, he will check players' answer, give them some punishments for theirs mistakes. On the other side, the psychiatrists try to understand what append and save the Prof. Wise.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A variant could be play where GM give roles to each players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Components:&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 1 24-page booklet for the game master (scenario, preparations, rules, solutions)&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 60 cards divided into 7 types of games (Amnesia, Bipolar, etc.)&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 1 psychiatric prescription&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 1 Rorschach test&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 1 map of the hospital&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 10 envelopes to conceal&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 6 psychological profiles to introduce a role play dimension.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
